# Static showcase of layouts.Form — aligned label/field rows.
#
# Regenerate:  vhs tapes/layouts-form.tape

Output docs/layouts-form.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 540
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "go run ./example/layouts/form"
Enter
Sleep 4500ms

Type "q"
Sleep 400ms
